description: Nutrition and health claims shall soon be harmonised at European level in order to better protect consumers. This Regulation establishes the authorisation procedures required to ensure that claims on food labelling, presentation and advertising are clear, concise and based on evidence accepted by the whole scientific community.  Data is collected and published in a register of accepted (and rejected) claims in accordance with legislation.
